1.2 Read data

df <- readRDS("../data/modelling_data_RSD.rds")

1.2.1 Tweak data

# Change order of levels in cluster
df$cluster <- factor(df$cluster, levels = c("sp", "sm", "sx", "spr"))
df <- subset(df, RSD != 0)

# create df without spr
df<- df[! df$cluster == "spr", ]
df <- droplevels(df)
levels(df$cluster)
## [1] "sp" "sm" "sx"
